819
01:21:14,528 --> 01:21:15,594
Evet.

820
01:21:19,192 --> 01:21:20,778
Gelir?

821
01:21:24,772 --> 01:21:26,279
Gelir mi?

822
01:21:28,119 --> 01:21:29,865
